  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Component\n\nFoundryup\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nThis is arguably two separate issues, but seems related enough to do both of these things at the same time:\r\n1. Running `foundryup` should also update `foundryup` so users can get `foundryup` fixes and features without needing to check that for updates separately\r\n2. `foundryup` should be rewritten in rust so we don't need to maintain a separate bash script\r\n\r\n(If separate issues are preferred, let me know and I can just close this and make two new ones)\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
